<h1>$title - Reference Documentation</h1>

<p>Ant Tasks Arsenal for Community</p>
<p>Provide ANT tasks to assist the development of java projects</p>

<h3>Requirements</h3>
<p>Ant 1.6.5 or newer</p>

<h3>Using My Tasks</h3>
<pre>
&lt;!-- This script uses my Ant Tasks --&gt;
&lt;project name=&quot;Example&quot; xmlns:atac=&quot;antlib:org.atac.ant&quot;&gt;

  &lt;taskdef uri=&quot;antlib:org.atac.ant&quot;
              resource=&quot;org/atac/ant/antlib.xml&quot;
              classpath=&quot;__path_to_atac_jar__/atac.jar&quot;/&gt;

  &lt;target name=&quot;atac-unix2dos-example&quot; description=&quot;Unix2Dos Example&quot;&gt;

    &lt;atac:unix2dos&gt;
      &lt;fileset dir=&quot;the_dir&quot;&gt;
        &lt;include name="**/*"/&gt;
      &lt;/fileset&gt;
    &lt;/atac:unix2dos&gt;

  &lt;/target&gt;

&lt;/project&gt;
</pre>


